column2: SELECT     m.search_id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.type, o.petroR5#_r,o.petroR5#Err_r,o.petroR9#_r,o.petroR9#Err_r,   o.err_u,o.err_g,o.err_r,o.err_i,o.err_z, z.z as redshift, z.zerr as redshift_err into mydb.cc2ph2 from MyDB.cc2 AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid    JOIN photoz as z ON n.objid=z.objid
